The paper deals with image and video recognition, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach presented in the paper involves online learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses feature selection and similarity measures, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper mentions a mixed text and image dataset, which suggests a possible connection to natural language processing (cs.CL).
